      "content": "Hey, I need some help with a few new listings. Can you write some catchy, high-end neighborhood descriptions for these two spots? I want them to really sell the \"vibe\" to potential buyers.\n\n1. Oak Ridge Estates: A quiet, traditional suburb with large lots, manicured lawns, and top-tier school districts. Very peaceful and established.\n\n2. West End District: A bustling, high-energy urban area with lots of street art, diverse food options, and a very active nightlife scene. Lots of movement and culture here.\n\nMake them sound really evocative!",
